metadata.name: DAOZER Legendary Membership
metadata.description:
**[DAOZER DAO](https://daozer.io)** - Thousands of crypto and NFT enthusiasts are coming together to benefit from the power of an organized community and collective network effect. 

DAOZER's mission is to create opportunities for its members as the NFT and crypto spaces grow through a fair, membership-based DAO supporting emerging talent, influencers, digital network marketers, patrons and its loyal community of supporters.
  
**LEGENDARY Membership** grants the following Perks:

- all perks from Epic Membership PLUS:
- FREE 1MM DAOZER utility token airdrop! (1,000,000 total) 
- LEGENDARY DAO voting rights
- 1 airdrop from all future DAOZER NFT mints
- LIMITED EDITION, LEGENDARY cardholders only NFT airdrops
- exclusive LEGENDARY Discord access
- exclusive LEGENDARY only events
- automatically entered all contests and giveaways
- additional LEGENDARY perks TBA as the community grows

*Terms of Sale Apply*

[daozer.io](https://daozer.io)
